{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"網頁小筆記","author":"Shizuku"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"73d60a16-0e08-5acd-8e4b-c467ba945708","excerpt":"本文會提到如何準備 Javascript 的開發環境還有神奇工具包 Parcel！ Blazing fast, zero configuration web application bundler\nParcel 是一個自動化專案打包工具，所有常見好用的工具如 Pug、SCSS 都幫你準備好 Node.js…","html":"<p>本文會提到如何準備 Javascript 的開發環境還有神奇工具包 Parcel！</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Blazing fast, zero configuration web application bundler\nParcel 是一個自動化專案打包工具，所有常見好用的工具如 Pug、SCSS 都幫你準備好</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>Node.js</h2>\n<p>畢竟程式只是一堆文字，要有人負責把文字轉換成實際的動作並執行，<a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/\">Nodejs</a> 就肩負這個重責大任。</p>\n<p>從官方網站選擇 LTS 版本下載並安裝後一路 Next 就能安裝完畢，確認是否安裝成功的話可以在 <code class=\"language-text\">命令提示字元</code> 輸入 <code class=\"language-text\">node --version</code> 看看有沒有出現版本資訊\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZWWIRQy.png\"></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ yarn global add parcel-bundler</code></pre></div>\n<h2>開發</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ parcel index.html --open</code></pre></div>\n<h2>打包</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ parcel build index.html -d [dest_dir] -o [filename]\n$ npx serve [dest_dir]</code></pre></div>\n<h2>快速開發工具</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Pug</li>\n<li>SCSS</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Pug</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>縮排</li>\n<li>屬性</li>\n<li>變數</li>\n<li>邏輯</li>\n<li>繼承，引入，函數…</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>縮排</h2>\n<p>以縮排代表元素階層</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"pug\"><pre class=\"language-pug\"><code class=\"language-pug\"><span class=\"token tag\">body</span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\">section.navbar</span> <span class=\"token plain-text\">logo</span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\">section.content</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\">.first</span> <span class=\"token plain-text\">paragraph one</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\">.second</span> <span class=\"token plain-text\">paragraph two</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\">input#name</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>navbar<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    logo\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>section</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>content<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>first<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      paragraph one\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>first<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      paragraph two\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>section</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>屬性</h2>\n<p>以括號表示屬性，空格或換行區分</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"pug\"><pre class=\"language-pug\"><code class=\"language-pug\"><span class=\"token tag\">input<span class=\"token attributes\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token string\">\"text\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\">input<span class=\"token attributes\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token string\">\"checkbox\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token string\">\"agreement\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">checked</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<label>\n<h2>變數 點我展開</h2>\n<input type=\"checkbox\" />\n<div>\n<p>可以使用 Javascript 並轉譯</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"pug\"><pre class=\"language-pug\"><code class=\"language-pug\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span><span class=\"token code\"> <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> inputType <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"checkbox\"</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\">label</span> <span class=\"token plain-text\">This is a #{inputType}</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\">input<span class=\"token attributes\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token attr-value\">inputType</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>輸出 Html</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>This is a checkbox<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>checkbox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code></pre></div>\n</div>\n</label>\n<h2>邏輯</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">each</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">if</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">switch</code>…</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"pug\"><pre class=\"language-pug\"><code class=\"language-pug\"><span class=\"token flow-control\"><span class=\"token branch keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\">div</span> <span class=\"token plain-text\">i'm block</span>\n<span class=\"token flow-control\"><span class=\"token branch keyword\">else</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\">span</span> <span class=\"token plain-text\">i'm inline</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>等號後面直接以 JS 執行</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"pug\"><pre class=\"language-pug\"><code class=\"language-pug\"><span class=\"token tag\">ul</span>\n  <span class=\"token flow-control\"><span class=\"token each\"><span class=\"token keyword\">each</span> value <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\">li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token code\"> value</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>輸出</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>3<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>SCSS</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>變數</li>\n<li>巢狀</li>\n<li>函數</li>\n<li>繼承</li>\n<li>引入</li>\n<li>算數</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>變數</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"scss\"><pre class=\"language-scss\"><code class=\"language-scss\"><span class=\"token variable\">$color</span> = red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">a </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>巢狀</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"scss\"><pre class=\"language-scss\"><code class=\"language-scss\"><span class=\"token selector\">.container </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token selector\">.title </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1.2em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>輸出</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"scss\"><pre class=\"language-scss\"><code class=\"language-scss\"><span class=\"token selector\">.container </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.container .title </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1.2em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>函數</h2>\n<p>自定函數， 以 <code class=\"language-scss\"><span class=\"token keyword\">@include</span></code> 使用</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"scss\"><pre class=\"language-scss\"><code class=\"language-scss\"><span class=\"token keyword\">@mixin</span> <span class=\"token function\">setBG</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\"><span class=\"token variable\">$color</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> black<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">div </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">@include</span> <span class=\"token function\">setBG</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>white<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>輸出</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> white<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>繼承</h2>\n<p>使用 <code class=\"language-scss\"><span class=\"token keyword\">@extend</span></code> 覆用 CSS!</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"scss\"><pre class=\"language-scss\"><code class=\"language-scss\"><span class=\"token selector\">.red-background </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">div </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">@extend</span> .red-background<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>輸出</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"scss\"><pre class=\"language-scss\"><code class=\"language-scss\"><span class=\"token selector\">.red-background </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">div </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>引入</h2>\n<p>引入其他 SCSS 檔案</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"scss\"><pre class=\"language-scss\"><code class=\"language-scss\"><span class=\"token keyword\">@import</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"clear\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">@import</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"font\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>算數</h2>\n<p>不用 <code class=\"language-text\">calc</code> 計算</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"scss\"><pre class=\"language-scss\"><code class=\"language-scss\"><span class=\"token selector\">div </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>300px/7<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/*font-size: calc(300px / 7);*/</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>輸出</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 42.8571428571px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>特色</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Code splitting</p>\n<ul>\n<li>dynamic import</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Hot Module Replacement</li>\n<li>\n<p>Production</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">parcel build index.html</code></li>\n<li>自動 <code class=\"language-text\">NODE_ENV=production</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Dynamic import</h2>\n<p>用到的時候才載入內容</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Promise</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"./pages/one\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>page<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  page<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// async/await</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> page <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"./pages/one\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\npage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Babel</h2>\n<p>引入 Babel 轉譯程式碼來支援各個瀏覽器</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ yarn add babel-polyfill</code></pre></div>\n<p>用到 async/await 語法的地方引入</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'babel-polyfill'</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">hello</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"開發環境配置 - Parcel","date":"March 06, 2019","description":"快速開始你的網頁專案","difficulty":"初階"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/dev-env-parcel/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/css-get-started/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS 基礎"}},"next":null}}